Package: TSOSGS
Type: package
Title: Training Set Optimization for Spatial Genomic Selection
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2025-07-02
Authors@R: c(
    person("Liang-Yu", "Chen", , "ryanc000@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Chen-Tuo", "Liao", , "ctliao@ntu.edu.tw", c("aut", "ths"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9777-3701")) )
Description: This package implements training set optimization for spatial 
    genomic selection using a genetic algorithm under the GBLUP model. 
    It includes both a Two-Stage and One-Stage Genetic Search algorithm, 
    with support for spatial correlation in the selection process.
Depends: R (>= 4.5.1), sommer (>= 4.4.1), MASS, stats, parallel
Imports: compiler
